snippet.title: Angry Birds Trilogy: New Anger Management Pack Available!
snippet.description:
New levels available for Angry Birds Trilogy! http://trilogy.angrybirds.com

For 130 new levels of fun, download the Anger Management pack now from Xbox LIVE or Playstation Network.

Angry Birds Trilogy flies the bestselling world phenomenon to console platforms for the first time with new features and graphics! Find out more at http://trilogy.angrybirds.com

Follow @angrybirds on Twitter at http://twitter.com/angrybirds
Like us on Facebook at http://facebook.com/angrybirds
Submit fan art to http://angrybirds.tumblr.com
